- **[I-220]** **Setter accept type asymmetry vs getter return type — pre-existing pattern T6/T7/T8/T9 共通 latent gap (PRD I-205 T9 Iteration v14 deep-deep review 由来、user 確定 2026-04-30)** [**L4** (Localized、TS asymmetric setter syntax は corner case、Hono reachability 低想定)] — `set value(v: T)` accepts T while `get value(): Option<T>` returns Option<T> の asymmetric class definition で、T9 `wrap_setter_value` は lhs_type = getter return type を見て Some-wrap、setter accept type と一致しない → Some(rhs) 渡しが setter expecting T に対し type mismatch (Rust E0308 catch)。

